data.name: ReadFips
data.value: select top(1) [STATE], COUNTY, LOCATION, STATE_DESC, COUNTY_DESC, LOCATION_DESC, STATE_ABBREVIATION, COUNTY_ABBR from CKT_FIPS where ([STATE] = @state) and (COUNTY = @county) and (LOCATION = @location)

data.name: ReadFipsTribAddress
data.value: select IDENTIFIER, FAX_EXTENSION, FAX_AREA_CD, PHONE_EXTENSION, AREA_CD, TYPE, STREET_1, STREET_2, CITY, [STATE], ZIP_CD, ZIP4, ZIP3, COUNTY, STREET_3, STREET_4, PROVINCE, POSTAL_CODE, COUNTRY, PHONE_NUMBER, FAX_NUMBER, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TSTAMP, LAST_UPDATED_BY, LAST_UPD_TSTAMP, FIP_STATE, FIP_COUNTY, FIP_LOCATION from CKT_FIPS_TRIB_ADDR where (FIP_STATE = @fipState) and (FIP_COUNTY = @fipCounty) and (FIP_LOCATION = @fipLocation)
